		<title>Diphtheria Situational Report (Week 7 Of 2025)</title>
		<link>https://www.nicd.ac.za/toxigenic-corynebacterium-diphtheriae-disease-situational-report-week-7-of-2025/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=toxigenic-corynebacterium-diphtheriae-disease-situational-report-week-7-of-2025</link>
		
